{"tid":503977,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"使用率十年跌9成　英國人妙招搶救「瀕危電話亭」","createTime":"2017-12-19T12:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T19:33:53.000Z","uid":41453,"like":259,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"395bb4e66657112a98aa0bff9cfcd8d515219146","tid":503977,"uid":41453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:14:05.000Z","msg":"英國電話亭數量於2002年攀上顛峰，當時共有9萬2000座遍布全英各地，自此之後數量即驟減，目前英國僅剩4萬2000座電話亭。現在每天由電話亭撥出的電話僅約3萬3000通，10年來減少90%。隨著流動電話的普及，英國經典的招牌紅色電話亭面臨「絕種」危機。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，英國當地的電話亭遭到棄置、破壞，甚至散發出陣陣尿騷味。而從商業角度來說，多數電話亭都虧錢，電話亭的維護費用每年卻高達500萬英鎊。因此，英國電信大廠英國電信集團（BT）計畫在2022年前再移除2萬座電話亭。<br />\n<br />\n不過，經過一番巧思改造，不少電話亭都被改造成圖書館、藝廊和資訊中心，其他則改造成咖啡簡餐店、帽子店甚至心臟去顫器使用點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2017/12/edix7q8ccdt895zu71vur3s0tubf0y.jpg?q=100&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F12%2Fedix7q8ccdt895zu71vur3s0tubf0y.jpg%3Fq%3D100%26w%3D1080&h=f851da08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時在布魯姆斯伯里廣場（Bloomsbury Square），每天都有很多上班族在改裝後的電話亭打發午餐，這座電話亭轉為配有小型冰箱和供人放置餐點平台的小站。亭內的招牌菜&mdash;&mdash;豐盛的沙拉&mdash;&mdash;特別受到喜歡坐在廣場花園享用午餐的客人喜愛。<br />\n<br />\n除了供餐的作用外，因其獨立而且私隱度高的外型，數百座電話亭也變身為自動提款機。而其他則改造成免費且網速超快的WiFi連接站，費用由廣告收益支付；也有電信集團考慮將電話亭改造成電動車充電站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2017/12/6qv70ryf8cjupft0mtzidaqtzlmon1.jpg?q=100&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F12%2F6qv70ryf8cjupft0mtzidaqtzlmon1.jpg%3Fq%3D100%26w%3D1080&h=e67c70b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了改用電話亭外，部分電話亭被授權經銷商修復並轉賣，但最便宜也賣到2,750英鎊。所以，也有英國電信集團推出「認養一座電話亭」（Adopt a Kiosk）計劃，以一英鎊出售給想要賦予電話亭新生命的當地社區或協會，當中涉及5千座電話亭。<br />\n<br />\n英國電信集團公用電話營運部門負責人 Mark Johnson 表示：「整個計畫的構想是把這個英國的文化遺產保存下來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2017/12/gyhvvmqyte6phkon4iskjkkrkqe3cw.jpg?q=100&amp;w=1080\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F12%2Fgyhvvmqyte6phkon4iskjkkrkqe3cw.jpg%3Fq%3D100%26w%3D1080&h=5c820edd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8697a0df48eaa27dca9af1ed1ed98a2b8892074f","tid":503977,"uid":11916,"like":220,"dislike":1,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:16:35.000Z","msg":"香港改建做爆房亭 應該好撚好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9beb36249acf6cacca1c9d7f1e8f6f91b4560855","tid":503977,"uid":4942,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"電話充電站有得諗wor<br />\n<br />\n$20 急叉15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n可惜都拆哂"},{"pid":"0d11db6b185480fe4b90f9b95e8cea35ff883307","tid":503977,"uid":15358,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港改建做爆房亭 應該好撚好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做劏房喇"},{"pid":"4cf2c11e082bfaf80a5312c46544ab9a2db82896","tid":503977,"uid":33443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港改建做爆房亭 應該好撚好賺&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n做劏房喇</blockquote><br />\n有得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2d0e044d7f1f496721497d03f6baf79fb68a02","tid":503977,"uid":25183,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"AED機同ATM<br />\n真係好貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f107306a7dc4a58d3d195be9dc365e237bf3ddb9","tid":503977,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港改建做爆房亭 應該好撚好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=